Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: Welcome to 35 Farragut where warmth and luxury meet ultimate design while showcasing breathtaking water views. Wake up and enjoy a sunrise that will start your day off with wonder. End your day with impromptu visits to the beach. This huge 2 bedroom 2 bath condo has grand spaces to enjoy or to seamlessly reconfigure for an additional room. Every detail was considered: gourmet kitchen with top of the line appliances, oversized island, specialized plumbing fixtures, jaw dropping custom closets throughout, steam shower, laundry room/home office, private exclusive home gym space, 2 car garage parking, direct elevator access, outdoor spaces, and the sandy beach right across the street- all in a welcoming South Boston-East side neighborhood setting. So convenient to vibrant restaurants, shopping, Boston and more!
